OL,3,CRoyal Mail delivery performance slips
OL,4,Cahead of second-class post overhaul
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has revealed that less than
OL,7,Fthree-quarters of first-class mail was
OL,8,Fdelivered on time over recent months,
OL,9,Fas it prepares to overhaul its letter
OL,10,Fdelivery services.
OL,12,FThe delivery giant said only 73.4% of
OL,13,Ffirst-class post was delivered the
OL,14,Fnext working day between June 20 and
OL,15,FSeptember 28.
OL,17,FIt also reported that 90.4% of second-
OL,18,Fclass mail was delivered within three
OL,19,Fworking days.
