OL,3,CRoyal Mail delivery performance slips
OL,4,Cahead of second-class post overhaul
OL,6,FThe latest quality of service report
OL,7,Fshows a declining performance since
OL,8,Fits annual results.
OL,10,FRoyal Mail was fined #21 million by
OL,11,Fregulator Ofcom for missing its mail
OL,12,Fdelivery targets for the 2024-25
OL,13,Ffinancial year.
OL,15,FDuring the year, it had delivered 77%
OL,16,Fof first-class mail and 92.5% of
OL,17,Fsecond-class mail on time.
OL,19,FThis was short of its respective 93%
OL,20,Fand 98.5% targets.
