OL,3,CRoyal Mail delivery performance slips
OL,4,Cahead of second-class post overhaul
OL,6,FRoyal Mail said it was taking action
OL,7,Fto improve the reliability of its
OL,8,Fservices, including by hiring more
OL,9,Fstaff and supporting its delivery
OL,10,Foffices.
OL,12,FIt is also preparing to introduce
OL,13,Fchanges that will see it scrap second-
OL,14,Fclass deliveries on Saturdays and
OL,15,Fswitch the service to every other
OL,16,Fweekday.
OL,18,FIt has been running pilots for the new
OL,19,Fdelivery model and is aiming to
OL,20,Fcontinue rolling it out from early
OL,21,Fnext year.
