OL,4,Cahead of second-class post overhaul
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FRoyal Mail's Chief Operating Officer
OL,12,FJamie Stephenson said: "Reliable
OL,13,Fdeliveries really matter to our
OL,14,Fcustomers, and they matter to us too.
OL,16,F"We're taking targeted action to
OL,17,Fimprove performance ` recruiting more
OL,18,Ffrontline staff, simplifying
OL,19,Foperations and investing in a new
OL,20,Fdelivery model, with early pilots
OL,21,Falready showing measurable results."
